# Which is better?

That, I think, would be a matter of opinion.  I tend to prefer the layout manager approach, as that&#39;s its domain of responsibility, however, with the custom component you could always ensure new components are set to the `0` position and change the rendering order (so that new components always appear on top)

Note: This answer is only for those looking to have many images on top of each other and control the order in which they are displayed dynamically.

